Posts.Content: Hi I am 54 and was dx in May 2007 and have just finished tmt.  I too keep hearing it is rare. I have seen others on this site with this type so it can't be that rare. I think it is seen less than an  estrogen driven type. I hope we see more information regarding this type. Hangin there and Good luck to you.  Let us see a cure for this disease.
Posts.Title: triple negative br. cancer

Posts.Content: Donna, I have just found a website that you may find helpful.  It is tnbcfoundation.org.  This website is for those of us who have triple negative ca. Hope this is useful to you.
